descriptionHtml:
A SweetFX preset tuned to my liking

Installation

1) Install [url={http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/23364}]{SweetFX Shader Suite}[/url]
2) Download my preset in the files section and extract the archive
3) Copy and paste the SweetFX_settings.txt file into your Skyrim folder, overwrite the file from step 1
4) Enjoy!
author: AgendaDysphoria
